Dear Nursery_A Admissions Team,

I’m Parent_E, checking in again in Round 14 as Nursery_A is still unmatched.

I understand you are allocating strictly by priority and are holding the place while awaiting responses from higher-priority families. To help me plan realistically, could you please confirm:
1) whether an offer has already been extended to a higher-priority family (and you’re awaiting their reply), and
2) the exact deadline/time by which you will treat that as a non-response and move to the next family on the waitlist.

If/when you are able to move to my position, I can accept immediately (same-day, within 1 hour if helpful) and complete all paperwork right away; we remain fully flexible on start date and schedule.

Thank you for your time,
